.\}
.PP
In such a case, your
\fIonly\fR
option for making the table available to MySQL again is to drop the table and re\-create it\&. You can use either the SQL statementDROP TABLE
or the
\fBndb_drop_table\fR
utility (see
ndb_drop_table(1)) to drop the table\&.
